wpt.cmt: From the layby, pass through a kissing gate to follow a path through woods.
wpt.desc: From the layby, pass through a kissing gate to follow a path through woods.

wpt.cmt: Soon, cross a ladder stile to the right into woodland. This is the beginning of the Interest Trail which leads through woodland.
wpt.desc: Soon, cross a ladder stile to the right into woodland. This is the beginning of the Interest Trail which leads through woodland.

wpt.cmt: Eventually the Interest Trail follows to the right of a driveway, with the Cage on a hill up to the left.
wpt.desc: Eventually the Interest Trail follows to the right of a driveway, with the Cage on a hill up to the left.

wpt.cmt: The Interest Trail soon leads down steps to a ladder stile. This is the start of Crow Wood. Cross the stile and continue to follow the trail.
wpt.desc: The Interest Trail soon leads down steps to a ladder stile. This is the start of Crow Wood. Cross the stile and continue to follow the trail.

wpt.cmt: Upon meeting a junction of paths, bear left.
wpt.desc: Upon meeting a junction of paths, bear left.

wpt.cmt: The trail soon emerges behind The Timber Yard. Walk around the left hand edge of the mill pond.
wpt.desc: The trail soon emerges behind The Timber Yard. Walk around the left hand edge of the mill pond.

wpt.cmt: Pass to the right of the main car park. At a fork in the driveway, bear right, to follow a driveway across a cattle grid and uphill.
wpt.desc: Pass to the right of the main car park. At a fork in the driveway, bear right, to follow a driveway across a cattle grid and uphill.

wpt.cmt: Soon a further car park is reached, at the entrance to Hase Bank Wood. Go through a gate, and follow the driveway down through Hase Bank Wood.
wpt.desc: Soon a further car park is reached, at the entrance to Hase Bank Wood. Go through a gate, and follow the driveway down through Hase Bank Wood.

wpt.cmt: Upon reaching the house at West Parkgate, pass through a gate and turn left down the driveway, and footpath to return to the starting point.
wpt.desc: Upon reaching the house at West Parkgate, pass through a gate and turn left down the driveway, and footpath to return to the starting point.

wpt.cmt: The path soon meets a driveway. Turn left up the driveway, passing a house named â€œWest Parkgateâ€.
wpt.desc: The path soon meets a driveway. Turn left up the driveway, passing a house named â€œWest Parkgateâ€.

wpt.cmt: Continue up the driveway, as it bears left, across a cattle grid. The driveway now levels out. Follow the driveway to Green Farm.
wpt.desc: Continue up the driveway, as it bears left, across a cattle grid. The driveway now levels out. Follow the driveway to Green Farm.

wpt.cmt: At Green Farm, where the driveway forks, follow the driveway to the right, to pass behind farm buildings. Take a narrow footpath to the right, which soon emerges at a ladder stile.
wpt.desc: At Green Farm, where the driveway forks, follow the driveway to the right, to pass behind farm buildings. Take a narrow footpath to the right, which soon emerges at a ladder stile.

wpt.cmt: Cross the ladder stile. You are now in Lyme Park. Follow the grassy path which leads diagonally uphill.
wpt.desc: Cross the ladder stile. You are now in Lyme Park. Follow the grassy path which leads diagonally uphill.

wpt.cmt: Where the grassy path meets a driveway, bear left. Very soon after, follow the narrow grassy path down to the left, away from the driveway. You should be heading directly across an open field towards a ladder stile in the high stone wall opposite, about 100 yards away.
wpt.desc: Where the grassy path meets a driveway, bear left. Very soon after, follow the narrow grassy path down to the left, away from the driveway. You should be heading directly across an open field towards a ladder stile in the high stone wall opposite, about 100 yards away.

wpt.cmt: The narrow grassy path heads down into a damp gully, then up again, to emerge at the ladder stile. Cross the ladder stile, and follow the path (signposted as â€œNCWâ€, the North Cheshire Way) along the top right hand edge of the field, with a high stone wall to your right.
wpt.desc: The narrow grassy path heads down into a damp gully, then up again, to emerge at the ladder stile. Cross the ladder stile, and follow the path (signposted as â€œNCWâ€, the North Cheshire Way) along the top right hand edge of the field, with a high stone wall to your right.

wpt.cmt: After crossing a few stiles, the path (still following the wall to the right) goes downhill. Upon reaching a driveway at the bottom of the hill, turn right.
wpt.desc: After crossing a few stiles, the path (still following the wall to the right) goes downhill. Upon reaching a driveway at the bottom of the hill, turn right.

wpt.cmt: Follow the driveway to Elmerhurst Cottage. Bear right through a gate. A sign indicates that you are entering Lyme Park.
wpt.desc: Follow the driveway to Elmerhurst Cottage. Bear right through a gate. A sign indicates that you are entering Lyme Park.
